;*************************
;*************************
;*************************

@NODE author "About the author"

Message from the author:

I'm a 19 year old guy from Gothenburg, Sweden.  I've been studying nature 
science for three years, and I'm hopefully about to move on to something 
more intriguing.  I like playing volleyball, IRCing  (look for me as 
volley!*volley@*.lls.se on #theend), and I just love trance/ambient music!
Check out my homepage (http://www.lls.se/~volley) for a lot more info. =)

Anyway, whether it's about MiniMail or Palantír, or about something 
completely different (*winks* to those of you who know what that might be),
feel free to write me at volley@lls.se.

NOTE: Please send questions and bugreports to 
@{" pontus.sjostrom@mailbox.swipnet.se " link distribution}!

"People would never dream of doing the things they dream of doing" @{I}Me @{UI}

"There are temptations so immense, that it requires both strength and 
 courage to give in to them" @{I}Oscar Wilde @{UI}

@ENDNODE

