@NODE todo "Todo"

There are no big future plans.  I am thinking about implementing a 
postpone/reedit function as well as some kind of script support, but...  no
promises can or will be made.

A program for easier configuration (with GUI) written by Jaden will probably
be released with the next version.  Thanks, Jaden! :)

In any case, watch out for Palantír, which will hopefully supersede MiniMail
soon.  Please have a look at http://www.lls.se/~volley for more information!

MiniMail has no known bugs..

@ENDNODE

